rmance out of it; it will be even lower on a laptop.  I'm not sure whether the laptop would be able to run the game, but if it did, I can be sure you wouldn't be pleased with the performance.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/372629.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br />FFXI - Carbuncle | Mikhalia WHM75/BLM75/MNK75/BRD75/DRG75 <br />WoW - Arygos | Eilemia 80 Warrior/Acriel 80 Warlock/Khaedra 80 Hunter <br /><span class="sm"> <br />Mikhalia: and FWIW, my posts are 95% helpful, informative, or funny. <br />Mikhalia: only 5% or less of my posts are utter crap. <br />Tyapex: 393 posts of utter crap... <br />Mikhalia: Sounds about right.</span> <br /> <br /><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Olorinus wrote:</div><div class="orig">I want Mikhalia to have fun - for example. I like playing with him.</div></div></div></div>
